# Keep Docker builds small and avoid baking runtime data/secrets.
*

!LICENSE
!MANIFEST.in
!README.md
!pyproject.toml
!requirements.txt
!setup.py

!raganything
!raganything/**

!work-space
!work-space/src
!work-space/src/**
!work-space/rag_core_service
!work-space/rag_core_service/**

# Runtime secrets and generated data must stay outside the image.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.venv
**/.venv/**
**/__pycache__
**/__pycache__/**
**/.pytest_cache
**/.pytest_cache/**
**/.local-data
**/.local-data/**
**/data
**/data/**
**/logs
**/logs/**
**/benchmark_outputs
**/benchmark_outputs/**
**/custom_storage
**/custom_storage/**
**/custom_uploads
**/custom_uploads/**
*.log
*.tmp
